                    data-isverify="False"
                    data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1083762/new_review">
                    <span>我要写书评</span>
                </a>
            <h2>
                    人类的群星闪耀时的书评 · · · · · ·

                    <span class="pl">( <a href="reviews">全部 4518 条</a> )</span>
            </h2>
